commands.chattranslate.translate.help:
§6[ChatTranslate]§f usage:

 §6/translator translator <translator>
  §7Set translator(Only Bing working.)

 §6/translator langFrom <from>
  §7Set from language.
 §6/translator langTo <to>
  §7Set to language.

 §6/translator start
  §7Start translator.
 §6/translator stop
  §7Stop translator.
